abstract: Digging deeper into the health care market, Intel has started selling its own Intel Reader device aimed at people who struggle to read printed material.

lead_paragraph: Intel’s push into the health care arena has the company going some unusual places.

headline.main: Intel Sells Its Own Reader for the Health Care Market
